{"tid":2102692,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"互動小說——《推倒世界》","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:53:24.000Z","uid":191300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3ad458bce49347a2f1d9cde4dc01bd3e8dcd8f","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"你是否想改變世界秩序&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n    目前，全球二百幾個國家同地區中，美國一枝獨秀毋庸置疑，中國、俄羅斯、日本、英國等傳統列強雖然野心勃勃，但受限於軍事同經濟實力，只能企埋一邊等候時機，至於落後國家，生存先係王道&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n        宜家，機會來了！！！！！！！！你係我大力支持之下，可以憑一己之力，推倒世界秩序！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事開始：<br />\n<br />\n   請選擇一個地點作為你的根據地<br />\n<br />\nA：美國&mdash;&mdash;黑人區<br />\nB：日本&mdash;&mdash;Av片場<br />\nC：印度&mdash;&mdash;恆河水底<br />\nD：朝鮮&mdash;&mdash;金與正閨房<br />\nE：中國&mdash;&mdash;新疆集中營<br />\nF：烏克蘭&mdash;&mdash;切爾諾貝爾輻射區<br />\nG：無國區&mdash;&mdash;南極大陸"},{"pid":"28da2117eb3808bcfc6b37ec6d2675a4e4cf88cc","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"3票！！！！當選！"},{"pid":"a76e7f34f6a078c8d04fa18c8c961e552c646ddf","tid":2102692,"uid":313719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"f35064de393c27b715e2510132cac10e295fcc54","tid":2102692,"uid":284127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"冇香港?"},{"pid":"87ad2cd8eb127589aa373bbee167ffa6cecc929a","tid":2102692,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8728b0106042b5f3993899b41cd8fa3181db3d5e","tid":2102692,"uid":315545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2cb081063ebb8be3320cff2522d345d8429ec8","tid":2102692,"uid":306052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"1f37dd4af47cd11527f7208525dad6044c2ce901","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T22:36:28.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"595afa923a095c05fb94e46d74170b9d924a56d7","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T22:37:34.000Z","msg":"樓豬 有幾多成機會 會棄故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf86a4fefa49f9312791fe4455d04b5d18977049","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"B 日本&mdash;&mdash;AV片場<br />\n<br />\n  故事開始。<br />\n<br />\n   作為故事的男主角，你名字的由來，事關於一段迂迴曲折的故事<br />\n<br />\n  時間追溯到2000年，也就是20年前，當時你的母親懷著你六個月，生活也算有滋有味。然而，一個晴天霹靂的惡耗傳來，你的時任父親因為千里迢迢走私自己被美國抓到，當場槍斃！<br />\n<br />\n    對於你父親的死，你的母親百感交集，走私自己這根本就是拋棄母子倆的惡劣行為，他的死應該感到開心，但又因為是最愛的人，又開心不起來，甚至是傷感。<br />\n<br />\n  父親死了，經濟來源也斷了，無依無靠的母親因為身懷著你難以找到正常工作，後來機遇巧合之下，經一位網上介紹，她去了日本AV拍攝現場，為了養活肚子中的你，或者說是讓你有未來，她豁出去了。<br />\n<br />\n     關於大肚婆的Av題材，你母親再適合不過了。<br />\n<br />\n 你母親機敏過人，經掐指一算，10－6＝4，也就算說還能賺取4個月的工資，她認為這4個月的工資足夠買營養品了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  可惜事以願違，她在拍攝第一場AV時，因為被內射而感到高潮後，此時他們的精子和你產生強烈的化學反應，導致你提前4個月出生了。<br />\n<br />\n    因為你提前4個月出生，又是在Av片場，再加上你父親姓浪，所以你母親特意幫你取名為&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    浪大條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n      20年後，你已茁壯成長，為了了解自己名字的由來，你走近年邁的母親旁，詢問了名字的由來。<br />\n<br />\n   鑒於你已經發育成功，她這時才把不堪回首往事一一告訴你，話畢，咬舌一百次自盡。<br />\n<br />\n      到死之前，你母親依然沒有說名字的由來，所以，你只知道自己浪大條，卻不知為何叫浪大條。<br />\n<br />\n  為了紀念她，你來到了日本，找到了那個屬於你出生地的Av片場。<br />\n<br />\n    母親的死讓你失去理智，那一刻，你在AV片場，注視著墻上的一隻螞蟻，堅信會用自己的實力報復社會！並且對自己聲稱Av片場就是自己的根據地！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    當晚，你在片場親手做了你最愛吃的螞蟻炒飯，邊吃邊想著如何推倒和平已久世界&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n   這宣告了故事正式開始。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推倒世界第一步，浪大條應該做的事是：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA：需要更多的力量，所以出門尋找志同道合的年輕人<br />\nB：去街市買把菜刀，先屠殺魚練練殺人手法<br />\nC：報警，謊稱遇到外星人<br />\nD：有錢才能執行更多行動，所以決定搶劫街邊乞丐。"},{"pid":"2378cfe512df4d4c96fd774aec66ba7a8d0def43","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:31:52.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"5a38a0af2bf5457595437dc5503a2a2a9184a38b","tid":2102692,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cad91f5c4b54a43149948d554eeecda83c0feb50","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97523d097b5b3aa6aef811440af772564535b852","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad91f5c4b54a43149948d554eeecda83c0feb50","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T22:06:34.000Z","msg":"已沉"},{"pid":"705204340a1ff051ed514d3370c28f68883f287e","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97523d097b5b3aa6aef811440af772564535b852","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad91f5c4b54a43149948d554eeecda83c0feb50","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T19:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T22:06:34.000Z","msg":"已沉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b349989833176dba7524de0f6c02fcf57cd808","tid":2102692,"uid":9256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:35:39.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"7eed1e0fb63cf8d3d2863bd018369e1c0556f575","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T20:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5837e3f66bf31c34288569ee739eec3093b2ca7","tid":2102692,"uid":307228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:05:32.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"a345d8b22c564aac1cfee3842739cbdb3c41f988","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:12:40.000Z","msg":"差一"},{"pid":"662978290585cea6a0047c147e1fcf3e98f4b862","tid":2102692,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a345d8b22c564aac1cfee3842739cbdb3c41f988","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:12:40.000Z","msg":"差一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"生物巴 有冇興趣玩故事接龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n類似咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[另類故事接龍] 我在藍星的日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2126121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2126121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}],"pinned":{"pid":"28da2117eb3808bcfc6b37ec6d2675a4e4cf88cc","tid":2102692,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:01:53.000Z","msg":"3票！！！！當選！"}}